{"tid":882664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[泡沫爆破] 美聯：業績差員工放無薪假3個月","createTime":"2018-10-30T09:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:49:01.000Z","uid":39092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00df45c0bebfe2cc80f72709434a92acbd6ebf2b","tid":882664,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:45:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/253052/%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE%E5%B7%AE%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%94%BE%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E5%81%873%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%91%E6%98%8E-%E6%9C%83%E6%B8%9B%E6%85%A2%E6%93%B4%E5%85%85%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F253052%2F%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25B8%25BE%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2596%25AA%25E5%2581%25873%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%2585%25A2%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%2585%2585%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E4%25BC%2590&d=%2Bi4EYpcX0ygC0tY6g2C%2FszPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=149d0765\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/253052/%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE%E5%B7%AE%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%94%BE%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E5%81%873%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%91%E6%98%8E-%E6%9C%83%E6%B8%9B%E6%85%A2%E6%93%B4%E5%85%85%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%90</a><br />\n<br />\n樓市進交投日趨萎縮，本港主要地產代理行之一的美聯物業，傳出要求集團佣金收入最低的100名地產代理，即「bottom榜」內部分員工放無薪假期。<br />\n<br />\n據《蘋果日報》報道，美聯將要求業績最差的10%員工必須離職；其後55%員工須自行申請放無薪假期至少三個月；而當中業績最高35%則可由主管擔保，下月1日生效。而放無薪假的代理，公司容許從事外間兼職工作，惟需申報及沒有利益衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2031794/org/2403a68e35db0074638b6c1f56c8f100.JPG/O6K5_chrXOum3kxNR9x75S-82ZLmv3lXMEJYiTBCWIk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2031794%2Forg%2F2403a68e35db0074638b6c1f56c8f100.JPG%2FO6K5_chrXOum3kxNR9x75S-82ZLmv3lXMEJYiTBCWIk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=25f18bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n布少明估計10月份一手成交宗數將跌40%。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業住宅部行政總裁布少明向《香港01》表示，該措施一直存在，只是因應近日樓市交投淡靜才決定嚴格執行，「目的是希望同事盡快做到生意。」未來公司亦會減慢擴充步伐，租約到期的分行會要求業主減租，屬非重要戰略的分行或不會續租。<br />\n<br />\n布少明又估計，10月份一手成交宗數，將由9月份的約2,000宗跌至1,200宗，跌幅達40%；二手亦由2,300宗降至1,700至1,800宗，跌幅逾21%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中原早前已透露，旗下有約200名代理今年至今都「食白果」，如果情況持續，今年底或未能獲續約，變相被裁！"},{"pid":"5e0530795d53361e86116f2e97468918b42c6d20","tid":882664,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3QzB4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3QzB4Y.jpg&h=e5087f70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e8397a10738584931230c43d21612aaa274cc46","tid":882664,"uid":167506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"b30c5e3eb5d8ea6e3564e56a7ecad1490743a9d4","tid":882664,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cd1cca15b752a596232be6568c031ac92ac1398","tid":882664,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}